<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Vim Spartan</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= action_cable_meta_tag %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all'%>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application'%>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <div class="nav-wrapper">
          <a href="/" class="brand-logo center">Vim Spartan</a>
          <a href="#" data-activates="mobile-nav" class="button-collapse"><i class="material-icons">menu</i></a>
          <ul id="nav-mobile" class="left hide-on-med-and-down">
            <li><a href="/home/training">연습 하기</a></li>
            <li><a href="/ranks">순위</a></li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="side-nav" id="mobile-nav">
            <li><a href="/home/training">연습 하기</a></li>
            <li><a href="/ranks">순위</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
      <%= yield %>
    </main>
    <!-- Modal Structure -->
    <div id="chint" class="modal bottom-sheet">
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <a href="#!" class=" modal-action modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat">닫기</a>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-content">
        <img src="/img/vim_command.jpg" class="responsive-img">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="mhint" class="modal bottom-sheet">
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <a href="#!" class=" modal-action modal-close waves-effect waves-green btn-flat">닫기</a>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-content">
        <img src="/img/vim_move.jpg" class="responsive-img">
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="page-footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col l6 s12">
            <h5 class="white-text">Vim Spartan</h5>
            <p class="grey-text text-lighten-4">서버 내에서 문서를 편집하기 위해 vim이나 emacs는 기본입니다. 누구나 vim에 입문할 수 있도록 필수적인 단축키를 스토리텔링 식으로 연습할 수 있습니다. 기초를 닦은 후 오른쪽에 있는 보다 많은 자료를 학습해보세요!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col l4 offset-l2 s12">
            <h5 class="white-text">치트시트</h5>
            <ul>
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3 modal-trigger" href="#chint">vim 명령어 단축키</a></li>
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3 modal-trigger" href="#mhint">vim 이동 단축키</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h5 class="white-text">추천 사이트</h5>
            <ul>
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3" href="http://www.joinc.co.kr/w/Site/Vim" target="_blank">vim 소개글</a></li>
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3" href="http://www.vimgolf.com/" target="_blank">vim 골프 : 최소한의 키로 목표달성하기</a></li>
              <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3" href="http://vim-adventures.com/" target="_blank">vim 어드벤처 : vim 단축키로 즐기는 게임</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copyright">
        <div class="container">
        © 2013 - 2016 Copyright Cycorld
        <a class="grey-text text-lighten-4 right" href="mailto:charleschoi87@gmail.com">charleschoi87 (at) gmail.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script>
      $(document).ready(function () {
        $(".button-collapse").sideNav();
        $('.modal-trigger').leanModal();
      });
    </script>
    <script>
      (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
      (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
